Homes: Seattle, Washington
Best-selling author Cassie Barden has been making art her whole life. She is inspired by contemporary art, design, illustration, technology, and anything handmade.
Adrienne Smitke grew up surrounded by crafts in a house full of handmade quilts and clothes. Drawing on her creative childhood, she studied illustration and graphic design in college.
